## Original CorrDiff Method Attribution

This project builds upon the CorrDiff method described in:

Subramanian, S., et al. (2023). "CorrDiff: Stochastic Correction Diffusion Models 
for Estimating Uncertainty in High-Resolution Image Synthesis." arXiv preprint 
arXiv:2309.15214. https://arxiv.org/abs/2309.15214

Please cite the original CorrDiff paper when using this work in research.
